sql:
SELECT AVG(gdp) AS average_gdp
FROM indicators
WHERE year = 2020;

external_knowledge:
* The "latest available data" refers to the data with the most recent last update date for each country and year;
* "Various indicators" include demographic, environmental, economic, and technological metrics;
* "User access patterns" encompass the frequency, data size, and duration of user sessions for each country;
* "Data quality checks" involve the number of checks, passed checks, and failed checks for each country.
